The Cycon Odyssey is a video game created for use with Cog Engine,
as part of the Cog Engine suite of software. This README contains
information which applies both to the game, and to the Cog Engine
itself.

Cog Engine documentation is an ongoing project. Please check the
homepage at http://cogengine.sourceforge.net for more information.


